data.description:
Assumable VA loan with 2.25% interest rate! What a great LOCATION -beautiful large corner lot in the highly sought-after gated community of Southwind in Bluewater Bay! This spectacular home has tons of curb appeal starting with a side-entry garage, paver driveway, walkways, & rear patio. You'll adore the southern style covered wrap around front porch surrounded by mature landscaping. Upon entering the front door, you can't help but notice the stunning hardwood floors, crown molding & a traditional wood staircase. stainless-steel fridge and dishwasher. There is also a breakfast area with French doors allowing in tons natural lighting and leads out to the back patio and spacious back yard with a peek-a-boo view of the 9th Marsh BWB golf course hole!! Your family and guests will enjoy the LARGE family area complete with a gas fireplace and built-in bookshelves. The first floor also has a half bath, under stair storage, and large laundry room complete w/cabinets & shelving.  The over-sized garage has a utility lift for convenient attic storage, which is climate controlled/insulated as well as cabinets and rail system for tools and bicycles.  

The 2nd story - has 4 beds/2 baths with the master bedroom boasting a huge walk-in closet and ensuite - double vanity, corner whirlpool tub and separate tiled shower. The other 3 bedrooms have sizable closets and hardwood flooring as well. 

The Bluewater Bay community boasts a Marina, beach, golfing, tennis, pickleball, walking trails, restaurants and more. Don't miss the opportunity to own this lovely home!
